  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >General Info</h2></h2></h2>Glowyjump is a 2D  platformer game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Unlocks</h2></h2>There are 50 levels.You have to reach hole to go next level.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You Have to Reach Hole.</h2></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics</h2></h2>Every platform has his own mechanics. Some are rotating, faster. <br>There are some gravity areas when you go inside this areas you can feel zero gravity.<br>Watch out meteors !<br><br>More levels and sound effects coming with first update !! Coming soon",
